{"id":"7e6f4b8bed0c43ea0a2fc3202d8a0397dd4163ee","url":"https://www.businessinsider.com/google-q2-2026-earnings-gemini-closing-in-chatgpt-1-billion-2026-7","title":"Google earnings: Gemini app nears 1 billion users, rivaling ChatGPT","site_name":"TechURLs","source":"Business Insider","byline":"Hugh Langley","excerpt":"Google has been closing the gap with ChatGPT, as its Gemini app hits 950 million monthly users.","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><section data-content-container=\"\" role=\"main\">\n\n  \n    \n  \n    <div data-load-strategy=\"disable-lazy\" data-component-type=\"post-top\">\n  \n        \n          <section id=\"post-headline\">\n            <h2>Google's Gemini app nips at ChatGPT's heels as it nears 1 billion users</h2>\n        \n          </section>\n          \n          \n          \n            <div data-component-type=\"post-byline\" data-track-marfeel=\"post-byline\" data-e2e-name=\"byline\">\n                      <p><span>By</span>\n                              \n                              \n                              \n                                <span data-e2e-name=\"Hugh Langley\">\n                              \n                                  <span>\n                                    <a data-e2e-name=\"byline-author-name\" href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/author/hugh-langley\">Hugh Langley</a>        \n                                <span data-disable-for-sooth-user=\"\" data-component-type=\"follow-button\" data-load-strategy=\"lazy\" role=\"tooltip\" data-tooltip-position=\"middle\" data-tooltip-active=\"false\" data-state=\"\" data-topic-type=\"author\" data-topic-slug=\"hugh-langley\" data-topic-link=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/author/hugh-langley\" data-topic-label=\"Hugh Langley\" data-topic-location=\"byline\" data-topic-shortened-label=\"Hugh\" data-topic-image=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;6556827336d588dc55d1f8f0&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;contentType&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Headshot of Hugh Langley&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:3394,&quot;source&quot;:&quot;Insider&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:2263},&quot;links&quot;:{&quot;self&quot;:&quot;https://i.insider.com/6556827336d588dc55d1f8f0&quot;}}\">\n                                  \n                                \n                                  <div>\n                                    <p>\n                                        You're currently following this author!\n                                 Want to unfollow? Unsubscribe via the link in your email.\n                                    </p>\n                                  </div>\n                                  \n                                </span>\n                                  </span>\n                                </span>  </p>\n                    </div>\n      </div>\n\n  <section>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n      <section id=\"post-body\" data-component-type=\"post-body\" data-load-strategy=\"exclude\" data-lock-content=\"\">\n            \n            \n            \n            <div data-component-type=\"post-hero\" data-load-strategy=\"exclude\">\n                  <figure data-type=\"img\" data-e2e-name=\"image-figure-image\" data-media-container=\"image\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ImageObject\">\n                      <div>\n                        <meta itemprop=\"contentUrl\" content=\"https://i.insider.com/6a2af71a24b3540ad29c21b9?width=1200\">\n                        <p><img src=\"https://i.insider.com/6a2af71a24b3540ad29c21b9?width=700\" srcset=\"https://i.insider.com/6a2af71a24b3540ad29c21b9?width=400&format=jpeg&auto=webp 400w, https://i.insider.com/6a2af71a24b3540ad29c21b9?width=500&format=jpeg&auto=webp 500w, https://i.insider.com/6a2af71a24b3540ad29c21b9?width=700&format=jpeg&auto=webp 700w, https://i.insider.com/6a2af71a24b3540ad29c21b9?width=1000&format=jpeg&auto=webp 1000w, https://i.insider.com/6a2af71a24b3540ad29c21b9?width=1300&format=jpeg&auto=webp 1300w, https://i.insider.com/6a2af71a24b3540ad29c21b9?width=2000&format=jpeg&auto=webp 2000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1280px) 900px\" alt=\"a standing man in a black quarter zip and glasses speaks\" decoding=\"sync\">\n                      </p></div>\n                  \n                    <span>\n                          <span>\n                            \n                            <label for=\"caption-drawer-btn\">\n                                      </label>\n                    \n                            <figcaption data-e2e-name=\"image-caption\">\n                              <span>Google CEO Sundar Pichai.</span>\n                              <span>\n                                <span data-e2e-name=\"image-source\" itemprop=\"creditText\">Bloomberg/Getty Images</span>          </span>\n                            </figcaption>\n                          </span>\n                    </span></figure>\n            </div>\n    \n    \n    \n            \n      \n              \n      \n      \n              \n              \n              \n              \n      \n            \n      \n        <section data-load-strategy=\"lazy\" data-component-type=\"image-modal\" data-track-content=\"\" data-post-type=\"story\" data-track-marfeel=\"post-body-content\">\n                  \n                      <p>Google's Gemini is nearing the big One Billion.</p><p>The company said on Wednesday that the Gemini AI app now has 950 million monthly active users. On the earnings call, CEO Sundar Pichai also said that daily active users have tripled in the past year.</p><p>That puts it close behind OpenAI's ChatGPT, which has around <a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/openai-projects-chatgpt-ad-growth-market-doubts-2026-7\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;body_link&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;tout_click&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\" rel=\"\">1 billion monthly users</a> per recent data from Sensor Tower.</p><p>To track Google's trajectory here, it said in October that the <a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/google-is-closing-the-gap-on-chatgpt-2025-10\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;body_link&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;tout_click&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\" rel=\"\">Gemini app</a> was seeing around 650 million monthly active users. In February, reporting its Q4 2025 earnings, <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://s206.q4cdn.com/479360582/files/doc_financials/2025/q4/2025q4-alphabet-earnings-release.pdf\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;click_type&quot;:&quot;other&quot;,&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;body_link&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;outbound_click&quot;}\" rel=\" nofollow\">Google said</a> that figure had risen to over 750 million.</p><p>Google has been rolling out more cost-friendly and faster models. This week, it rolled out three&#160;models, including its&#160;<a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/google-gemini-35-pro-flash-cyber-lite-speed-token-price-2026-7\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;body_link&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;tout_click&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\" rel=\"\">Gemini 3.6 Flash model</a>, which the company said is better at tasks such as coding than its predecessor while using fewer tokens,&#160;making it more cost-effective.</p><p>Google's new frontier <a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/rivals-mock-google-gemini-3-5-pro-delay-2026-7\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;body_link&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;tout_click&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\" rel=\"\">3.5 Pro model</a> is still delayed, even as Google this week teased that early work on Gemini 4 had started. These latest user numbers on Gemini suggest that it's still scooping up users quite nicely.</p>\n                  \n                  \n                  </section>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n      </section>\n\n    \n    <!-- Included desktop \"post-aside\" -->  \n\n    \n      \n      <section data-component-type=\"post-bottom\" data-load-strategy=\"exclude\" data-track-marfeel=\"post-bottom\">\n        <section>\n    \n    \n            \n            \n    \n              \n                \n                \n                <section data-component-type=\"dad-related-posts\" data-delay-third-party-scripts=\"true\" data-size=\"4\" data-min-size=\"3\" data-container-index=\"\" data-included-verticals=\"tech\" data-placement=\"post-bottom\" data-track-marfeel=\"dad-related-posts-post-bottom\" data-excluded-verticals=\"bi-video\" data-root-margin=\"250px 0px\" data-track-view=\"{&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;end_of_article_recirc&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;subscription_experience&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\">\n                    <P>\n                      <h2>\n                        Read next\n                      </h2>\n                    </P>\n              \n              \n                  \n                </section>\n          \n          \n        <div data-component-type=\"post-bottom-authors\" data-load-strategy=\"exclude\" data-track-view=\"{&quot;subscription_experience&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;author_bio&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;module_in_view&quot;}\" data-track-click-shared=\"{&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;author_bio&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;navigation&quot;}\">\n                <a href=\"https://www