Unsubscribe via the link in your email. Google AI Generative AI More Big Tech","fetched_at":"2026-07-24T00:37:37.142Z","ok":true,"blocks":[{"html_en":"<h2>Google's Gemini app nips at ChatGPT's heels as it nears 1 billion users</h2>","sentences":[{"en":"Google's Gemini app nips at ChatGPT's heels as it nears 1 billion users","zh":"谷歌 Gemini 应用紧随 ChatGPT 脚步，用户数量接近 10 亿"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>By</span>\n                              \n                              \n                              \n                                <span data-e2e-name=\"Hugh Langley\">\n                              \n                                  <span>\n                                    <a data-e2e-name=\"byline-author-name\" href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/author/hugh-langley\">Hugh Langley</a>        \n                                <span data-disable-for-sooth-user=\"\" data-component-type=\"follow-button\" data-load-strategy=\"lazy\" role=\"tooltip\" data-tooltip-position=\"middle\" data-tooltip-active=\"false\" data-state=\"\" data-topic-type=\"author\" data-topic-slug=\"hugh-langley\" data-topic-link=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/author/hugh-langley\" data-topic-label=\"Hugh Langley\" data-topic-location=\"byline\" data-topic-shortened-label=\"Hugh\" data-topic-image=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;6556827336d588dc55d1f8f0&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;contentType&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Headshot of Hugh Langley&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:3394,&quot;source&quot;:&quot;Insider&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:2263},&quot;links&quot;:{&quot;self&quot;:&quot;https://i.insider.com/6556827336d588dc55d1f8f0&quot;}}\">\n                                  \n                                \n                                  <div>\n                                    <p>\n                                        You're currently following this author!\n                                 Want to unfollow? Unsubscribe via the link in your email.\n                                    </p>\n                                  </div>\n                                  \n                                </span>\n                                  </span>\n                                </span>  </p>","sentences":[{"en":"By Hugh Langley You're currently following this author!","zh":"作者：Hugh Langley 您目前正在关注该作者！"},{"en":"Want to unfollow?","zh":"想要取消关注吗？"},{"en":"Unsubscribe via the link in your email.","zh":"通过电子邮件中的链接取消订阅。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>\n                                        You're currently following this author!\n                                 Want to unfollow? Unsubscribe via the link in your email.\n                                    </p>","sentences":[{"en":"You're currently following this author!","zh":"您目前正在关注该作者！"},{"en":"Want to unfollow?","zh":"想要取消关注吗？"},{"en":"Unsubscribe via the link in your email.","zh":"通过电子邮件中的链接取消订阅。"}]},{"html_en":"<figcaption data-e2e-name=\"image-caption\">\n                              <span>Google CEO Sundar Pichai.</span>\n                              <span>\n                                <span data-e2e-name=\"image-source\" itemprop=\"creditText\">Bloomberg/Getty Images</span>          </span>\n                            </figcaption>","sentences":[{"en":"Google CEO Sundar Pichai.","zh":"谷歌首席执行官桑达尔·皮查伊。"},{"en":"Bloomberg/Getty Images","zh":"彭博社/盖蒂图片社"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Google's Gemini is nearing the big One Billion.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Google's Gemini is nearing the big One Billion.","zh":"谷歌的双子座已接近十亿大关。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>The company said on Wednesday that the Gemini AI app now has 950 million monthly active users. On the earnings call, CEO Sundar Pichai also said that daily active users have tripled in the past year.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"The company said on Wednesday that the Gemini AI app now has 950 million monthly active users.","zh":"该公司周三表示，Gemini AI 应用程序目前拥有 9.5 亿月活跃用户。"},{"en":"On the earnings call, CEO Sundar Pichai also said that daily active users have tripled in the past year.","zh":"在财报电话会议上，首席执行官桑达尔·皮查伊还表示，过去一年每日活跃用户数量增加了两倍。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>That puts it close behind OpenAI's ChatGPT, which has around <a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/openai-projects-chatgpt-ad-growth-market-doubts-2026-7\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;body_link&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;tout_click&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\" rel=\"\">1 billion monthly users</a> per recent data from Sensor Tower.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"That puts it close behind OpenAI's ChatGPT, which has around 1 billion monthly users per recent data from Sensor Tower.","zh":"这使得它紧随 OpenAI 的 ChatGPT 之后，根据 Sensor Tower 的最新数据，ChatGPT 每月约有 10 亿用户。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>To track Google's trajectory here, it said in October that the <a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/google-is-closing-the-gap-on-chatgpt-2025-10\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;body_link&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;tout_click&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\" rel=\"\">Gemini app</a> was seeing around 650 million monthly active users. In February, reporting its Q4 2025 earnings, <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://s206.q4cdn.com/479360582/files/doc_financials/2025/q4/2025q4-alphabet-earnings-release.pdf\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;click_type&quot;:&quot;other&quot;,&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;body_link&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;outbound_click&quot;}\" rel=\" nofollow\">Google said</a> that figure had risen to over 750 million.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"To track Google's trajectory here, it said in October that the Gemini app was seeing around 650 million monthly active users.","zh":"为了追踪谷歌的发展轨迹，谷歌在 10 月份表示，Gemini 应用程序的月活跃用户约为 6.5 亿。"},{"en":"In February, reporting its Q4 2025 earnings, Google said that figure had risen to over 750 million.","zh":"今年 2 月，谷歌在公布 2025 年第四季度财报时表示，这一数字已升至超过 7.5 亿。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Google has been rolling out more cost-friendly and faster models. This week, it rolled out three&#160;models, including its&#160;<a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/google-gemini-35-pro-flash-cyber-lite-speed-token-price-2026-7\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;body_link&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;tout_click&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\" rel=\"\">Gemini 3.6 Flash model</a>, which the company said is better at tasks such as coding than its predecessor while using fewer tokens,&#160;making it more cost-effective.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Google has been rolling out more cost-friendly and faster models.","zh":"谷歌一直在推出更经济、更快速的模型。"},{"en":"This week, it rolled out three models, including its Gemini 3.6 Flash model, which the company said is better at tasks such as coding than its predecessor while using fewer tokens, making it more cost-effective.","zh":"本周，它推出了三种型号，包括 Gemini 3.6 Flash 型号，该公司表示，该型号比其前身更擅长编码等任务，同时使用更少的代币，使其更具成本效益。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Google's new frontier <a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/rivals-mock-google-gemini-3-5-pro-delay-2026-7\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;body_link&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;tout_click&quot;,&quot;index&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\" rel=\"\">3.5 Pro model</a> is still delayed, even as Google this week teased that early work on Gemini 4 had started. These latest user numbers on Gemini suggest that it's still scooping up users quite nicely.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Google's new frontier 3.5 Pro model is still delayed, even as Google this week teased that early work on Gemini 4 had started.","zh":"尽管谷歌本周表示 Gemini 4 的早期工作已经开始，但谷歌的新 Frontier 3.5 Pro 型号仍然被推迟。"},{"en":"These latest user numbers on Gemini suggest that it's still scooping up users quite nicely.","zh":"Gemini 的这些最新用户数据表明，它仍然在很好地吸引用户。"}]},{"html_en":"<h2>\n                        Read next\n                      </h2>","sentences":[{"en":"Read next","zh":"阅读下一篇"}]},{"html_en":"<p><a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/author/hugh-langley\" data-track-click=\"{&quot;index&quot;:1}\">Hugh Langley</a>\n        \n                \n          <span data-disable-for-sooth-user=\"\" data-component-type=\"follow-button\" data-load-strategy=\"lazy\" role=\"tooltip\" data-tooltip-position=\"middle\" data-tooltip-active=\"false\" data-state=\"\" data-topic-type=\"author\" data-topic-slug=\"hugh-langley\" data-topic-link=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/author/hugh-langley\" data-topic-label=\"Hugh Langley\" data-topic-location=\"author_bio\" data-topic-shortened-label=\"Hugh\" data-topic-image=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;6556827336d588dc55d1f8f0&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;contentType&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Headshot of Hugh Langley&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:3394,&quot;source&quot;:&quot;Insider&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:2263},&quot;links&quot;:{&quot;self&quot;:&quot;https://i.insider.com/6556827336d588dc55d1f8f0&quot;}}\">\n            \n          \n            <div>\n              <p>\n                  You're currently following this author!\n           Want to unfollow? Unsubscribe via the link in your email.\n              </p>\n            </div>\n            \n          </span>\n            </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Hugh Langley You're currently following this author!","zh":"休·兰利 您目前正在关注该作者！"},{"en":"Want to unfollow?","zh":"想要取消关注吗？"},{"en":"Unsubscribe via the link in your email.","zh":"通过电子邮件中的链接取消订阅。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>\n                  You're currently following this author!\n           Want to unfollow? Unsubscribe via the link in your email.\n              </p>","sentences":[{"en":"You're currently following this author!","zh":"您目前正在关注该作者！"},{"en":"Want to unfollow?","zh":"想要取消关注吗？"},{"en":"Unsubscribe via the link in your email.","zh":"通过电子邮件中的链接取消订阅。"}]},{"html_en":"<li>\n                  <a data-track-click=\"\" href=\"/category/google\" title=\"Google\">Google</a>\n                </li>","sentences":[{"en":"Google","zh":"谷歌"}]},{"html_en":"<li>\n                  <a data-track-click=\"\" href=\"/category/ai\" title=\"AI\">AI</a>\n                </li>","sentences":[]},{"html_en":"<li>\n                  <a data-track-click=\"\" href=\"/category/generative-ai\" title=\"Generative AI\">Generative AI</a>\n                </li>","sentences":[{"en":"Generative AI","zh":"生成式人工智能"}]},{"html_en":"<li>\n                  <span data-track-click=\"{&quot;click_text&quot;:&quot;More&quot;,&quot;click_path&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\">More </span>\n                </li>","sentences":[]},{"html_en":"<li>\n                    <a data-track-click=\"\" href=\"/category/big-tech\" title=\"Big Tech\">Big Tech</a>\n                  </li>","sentences":[{"en":"Big Tech","zh":"大型科技公司"}]}],"translated":true,"content_html_zh":"<div class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><section data-content-container=\"\" role=\"main\">\n\n  \n    \n  \n    <div data-load-strategy=\"disable-lazy\" data-component-type=\"post-top\">\n  \n        \n          <section id=\"post-headline\">\n            <h2>谷歌 Gemini 应用紧随 ChatGPT 脚步，用户数量接近 10 亿</h2>\n        \n          </section>\n          \n          \n          \n            <div data-component-type=\"post-byline\" data-track-marfeel=\"post-byline\" data-e2e-name=\"byline\">\n                      <p>作者：Hugh Langley 您目前正在关注该作者！ 想要取消关注吗？ 通过电子邮件中的链接取消订阅。</p>\n                    </div>\n      </div>\n\n  <section>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n      <section id=\"post-body\" data-component-type=\"post-body\" data-load-strategy=\"exclude\" data-lock-content=\"\">\n            \n            \n            \n            <div data-component-type=\"post-hero\" data-load-strategy=\"exclude\">\n                  <figure data-type=\"img\" data-e2e-name=\"image-figure-image\" data-media-container=\"image\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ImageObject\">\n                      <div>\n                        <meta itemprop=\"contentUrl\" content=\"https://i.insider.com/6a2af71a24b3540ad29c21b9?width=1200\">\n                        <p><img src=\"https://i.insider.com/6a2af71a24b3540ad29c21b9?width=700\" srcset=\"https://i.insider.com/6a2af71a24b3540ad29c21b9?width=400&format=jpeg&auto=webp 400w, https://i.insider.com/6a2af71a24b3540ad29c21b9?width=500&format=jpeg&auto=webp 500w, https://i.insider.com/6a2af71a24b3540ad29c21b9?width=700&format=jpeg&auto=webp 700w, https://i.insider.com/6a2af71a24b3540ad29c21b9?width=1000&format=jpeg&auto=webp 1000w, https://i.insider.com/6a2af71a24b3540ad29c21b9?width=1300&format=jpeg&auto=webp 1300w, https://i.insider.com/6a2af71a24b3540ad29c21b9?width=2000&format=jpeg&auto=webp 2000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1280px) 900px\" alt=\"a standing man in a black quarter zip and glasses speaks\" decoding=\"sync\">\n                      </p></div>\n                  \n                    <span>\n                          <span>\n                            \n                            <label for=\"caption-drawer-btn\">\n                                      </label>\n                    \n                            <figcaption data-e2e-name=\"image-caption\">谷歌首席执行官桑达尔·皮查伊。 彭博社/盖蒂图片社</figcaption>\n                          </span>\n                    </span></figure>\n            </div>\n    \n    \n    \n            \n      \n              \n      \n      \n              \n              \n              \n              \n      \n            \n      \n        <section data-load-strategy=\"lazy\" data-component-type=\"image-modal\" data-track-content=\"\" data-post-type=\"story\" data-track-marfeel=\"post-body-content\">\n                  \n                      <p>谷歌的双子座已接近十亿大关。</p><p>该公司周三表示，Gemini AI 应用程序目前拥有 9.5 亿月活跃用户。 在财报电话会议上，首席执行官桑达尔·皮查伊还表示，过去一年每日活跃用户数量增加了两倍。</p><p>这使得它紧随 OpenAI 的 ChatGPT 之后，根据 Sensor Tower 的最新数据，ChatGPT 每月约有 10 亿用户。</p><p>为了追踪谷歌的发展轨迹，谷歌在 10 月份表示，Gemini 应用程序的月活跃用户约为 6.5 亿。 今年 2 月，谷歌在公布 2025 年第四季度财报时表示，这一数字已升至超过 7.5 亿。</p><p>谷歌一直在推出更经济、更快速的模型。 本周，它推出了三种型号，包括 Gemini 3.6 Flash 型号，该公司表示，该型号比其前身更擅长编码等任务，同时使用更少的代币，使其更具成本效益。</p><p>尽管谷歌本周表示 Gemini 4 的早期工作已经开始，但谷歌的新 Frontier 3.5 Pro 型号仍然被推迟。 Gemini 的这些最新用户数据表明，它仍然在很好地吸引用户。</p>\n                  \n                  \n                  </section>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n      </section>\n\n    \n    <!-- Included desktop \"post-aside\" -->  \n\n    \n      \n      <section data-component-type=\"post-bottom\" data-load-strategy=\"exclude\" data-track-marfeel=\"post-bottom\">\n        <section>\n    \n    \n            \n            \n    \n              \n                \n                \n                <section data-component-type=\"dad-related-posts\" data-delay-third-party-scripts=\"true\" data-size=\"4\" data-min-size=\"3\" data-container-index=\"\" data-included-verticals=\"tech\" data-placement=\"post-bottom\" data-track-marfeel=\"dad-related-posts-post-bottom\" data-excluded-verticals=\"bi-video\" data-root-margin=\"250px 0px\" data-track-view=\"{&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;end_of_article_recirc&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;subscription_experience&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;}\">\n                    <p>\n                      </p><h2>阅读下一篇</h2>\n                    <p></p>\n              \n              \n                  \n                </section>\n          \n          \n        <div data-component-type=\"post-bottom-authors\" data-load-strategy=\"exclude\" data-track-view=\"{&quot;subscription_experience&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;product_field&quot;:&quot;bi_value_unassigned&quot;,&quot;element_name&quot;:&quot;author_bio&quot;,&quot;event&quot;:&quot;module_in_vi